title: Leona's X Factor.avi
description:
Hour and a half documentary about Leona Lewis, one of the greatest singers of all time. Leona was discovered from a British tv-series called The X Factor (music talent show like Pop Idol) which she won under Christmas 2006. First half of this documentary concentrates on Leona&#039;s actual performances in that competition. Several performances are shown completely without forgetting valuable judge comments ("legendary" Simon Cowell is also there!). For me this first half really gives the most because Leona&#039;s emotional interpretations of old classics are simply incredible. I can&#039;t remember ever seeing or hearing anything as beautiful. The second half consists "Winners&#039; Week" type of material with interviews etc.
